            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Genio <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>indicis</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>pro salute <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Impp</abbr><ex>eratorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caess</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Septimi <lb n="4"/>Severi Pii Pertinacis <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli An<lb break="no" n="6"/>tonini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> Felicis <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Par</abbr><ex>thici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>annici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ger</abbr><ex>manici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>et Iuliae Augustae <lb n="9"/>matris Augusti <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>et <expan><abbr>castror</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dedicant</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Anicio Fausto <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>des</abbr><ex>ignato</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Arranius Datus <lb n="14"/>signifer <lb n="15"/>ex HS III <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ummum</ex></expan> de suo <lb n="16"/>posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 6-7: Felicis Par. Brit. Ger. max steht über der eradierten Erwähnung Getas. Z. 9: Augusti n. statt ursprünglichem Augustorum. Datierung: Q. Anicius Faustus wurde 197 oder 198 n. Chr. zum consul designiert.</p>
